<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN"
	 "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
	  xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
	  xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal">
	<head>
		<meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
		<title>NextThought Password Reset</title>
		<style metal:define-macro="style">
			#green-bar {
			background-color: #89be3c;
			width: 100%;
			height: 5px;
			margin-left: -30px;
			padding-right: 40px;
			}
			#logo-bar {
			margin-top: 20px;
			margin-bottom: 30px;
			}
			body {
			margin-left: 30px;
			margin-right: 0px;
			font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
			font-size: 14pt;
			line-height: 20pt;
			color: #757474;
			}
			.normal-text {
			margin-left: 30px;
			margin-right: 0px;
			font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
			font-size: 14pt;
			line-height: 20pt;
			color: #757474;
			}
			a {
			text-decoration: none;
			color: #3fb3f6;
			}
			.tterm, strong {
			font-weight: bold;
			color: #494949;
			}
			.tterm-color {
			font-weight: bold;
			color: #3fb3f6;
			}
			h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
			font-weight: bold;
			font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
			color: #757474;
			margin-left: 30px;
			}
			h1 {
			font-size: 16pt;
			}
			h2 {
			font-size: 14pt;
			}
			body p {
			margin-right: 30px;
			margin-left: 30px;
			font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
			font-size: 14pt;
			line-height: 20pt;
			color: #757474;
			}
			.pnormal-text {
			margin-left: 30px;
			margin-right: 30px;
			font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
			font-size: 14pt;
			line-height: 20pt;
			color: #757474;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body class="normal-text">
		<div metal:define-macro="header">
		<div id="green-bar" style="background-color: #89be3c; width: 100%; height: 5px; margin-left: -30px; padding-right: 40px;"></div>
		<div id="logo-bar">
			<img src="http://d2ixlfeu83tci.cloudfront.net/images/email_logo.png" width="177" height="25"
			alt="NextThought Logo" />
		</div>
		</div>
		<p>Hello <span tal:content="options/user/username">username</span>.</p>

		<p>
			You are receiving this notification because you (or
			someone pretending to be you) requested your
			NextThought password for  <span
			tal:content="options/user/username">username</span>
			on <a href="http://nextthought.com"
				  tal:attributes="href request/application_url"
				  tal:content="request/application_url">http://nextthought.com</a>
			be reset.

		</p>
		<p>To reset your password, follow these steps:
		<ol>
			<li>Click the link below to open a new and secure browser
			window.</li>
			<li>Enter the requested information and follow the
			instructions to reset your password.</li>
		</ol>
		</p>
		<p>
			Reset your password:<br /> <a href="https://nextthought.com"
									tal:attributes="href options/reset_url"
									tal:content="options/reset_url">https://reset?id=foo</a>
		</p>
		<p>
			If you did not request this reset, you can safely
			disregard this email.
		</p>
		<p>
		For help, you can email us at <a href="mailto:support@nextthought.com">support@nextthought.com</a>.
		</p>

		<p>
			Sincerely, <br />
			NextThought
		</p>

	</body>
</html>
